{"tid":430842,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"ADHD + 中度抑鬱想睇醫生求請教..","createTime":"2017-10-10T07:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T04:39:54.000Z","uid":117929,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"efd4db76cdb0c00be8f07463ddb0875b622b9f67","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"巴打、內文有少少長、<br />\n但希望您地耐心睇完的話可以比少少意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔開心左好耐、<br />\n計計埋埋都有兩年以上。<br />\n<br />\n我唔會無端端喊果d、<br />\n但係每日都好唔開心 感覺人生好灰暗<br />\n我無自殺既念頭、<br />\n但感覺人生、將來無咩野好憧景<br />\n感覺人生好無趣、好無意義。<br />\n死左都不太可惜果種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n訓得OK, 無咩失眠問題、<br />\n但有嗜睡問題、<br />\n我愈來愈少講野、<br />\n有時個人會好呆、<br />\n記性明顯差左好多、<br />\n無論係訓8個鐘好、定係4個半鍾好、都好累好累<br />\n<br />\n我一直都唔想面對有一日要去睇醫生依個情況<br />\n我有試過食EPA補充劑再加跑步去解決一直情緒低落既問題、<br />\n跑完係有感覺好左、<br />\n但之後又變番唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n我想去見精神科醫生、私家果d。<br />\n我知道如果去睇政府醫生、我響公立醫院既病歷就會有抑鬱症(如果醫生確診)跟我一世、以後一世唔駛考紀律部隊。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係諗住考紀律部隊、我本身係會計師。<br />\n如果我自己去睇私家醫生開d抗抑鬱藥試下食。<br />\n依個情況之下、我會唔會響個人病歷中留有被確診抑鬱性/ 情緒病紀錄？<br />\n因為我將來可能會考財金類既公務員、或者移民之類、怕因爲咁樣成世就花左個紀錄。"},{"pid":"e7d6e04877a24a331b1e502fe0c822a7f0fa92d5","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"自己補充一下：<br />\n<br />\n我指我想睇果d私家精神病醫生係類似 維X心理醫療中心果d...或者其他私人執業果d精神科 果d...而唔係普通門診/ 家庭醫生.."},{"pid":"dd42aa29c53b91e653efefa675b97a1f7cca40a4","tid":430842,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"點解要醫"},{"pid":"0ab79f18c60b7d31cba881b45ae6a8859a12897b","tid":430842,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"呢個係你自己既世界觀黎 有咩唔好 有咩錯"},{"pid":"711a31fa6be22bbf41ec6419ff3c4a7732c73c06","tid":430842,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己補充一下：<br />\n<br />\n我指我想睇果d私家精神病醫生係類似 維X心理醫療中心果d...或者其他私人執業果d精神科 果d...而唔係普通門診/ 家庭醫生..</blockquote><br />\n睇私家既，初步問左醫生意見先"},{"pid":"86e43db42d299c4d5bd35fddc55416cefacf669b","tid":430842,"uid":2720,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"ADHD都算 冇睇過醫生中乜撚嘢度抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba93e03de56c842e812117a4d711a8875fcf07c","tid":430842,"uid":22855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"為左考公務員唔去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分清楚係你生命入面 邊樣係莊 邊樣係閒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df761ac87ba17e315bcfde363b6e71f7c82dc771","tid":430842,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29fa8c66c955c6ea122e990393e4a4c82ea50913","tid":430842,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"咁似我嘅，我係咪都要睇醫生其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f83ed18e92fbdba6132c533fba8dbf26d45e42","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"邊條pk仔負皮我、有沒有人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0cc6ab2ca965bc07970e41bf332531f7e0bfa2","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似我嘅，我係咪都要睇醫生其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你同我一樣情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d27401d8971d5ebb221dd162ff458ac37762142","tid":430842,"uid":80565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"我同你差唔多情況"},{"pid":"6c55182d7f9536808af8331f5fa4b99b2d5bce42","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為左考公務員唔去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分清楚係你生命入面 邊樣係莊 邊樣係閒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我係HA既病紀錄可以俾人知既咩？呢d唔係犯罪記錄，係我既私隱黎wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去政府聯網醫院睇實睇到你病歷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e043dbf90e62a6aaacf1e39c46c8158b938fd","tid":430842,"uid":126736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:38:32.000Z","msg":"大部份香港人都係咁<br />\n利申 我都係"},{"pid":"2ea9e0b3849d178b9788654849b3fe9e558d5954","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同你差唔多情況</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同病相憐"},{"pid":"acbb54390f68eda18f1d634e049b746639187303","tid":430842,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊條pk仔負皮我、有沒有人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正評返你 唔好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4769531166160936a79eaa0ee3135c640d904f3","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大部份香港人都係咁<br />\n利申 我都係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好似每幾個香港人之中就有一個有情緒病徵狀。差在有無去睇醫生/ 有無見報/ 有幾嚴重架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b2201602e962849b1f68c04845fa3ce5e83ebb","tid":430842,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"搵therapist傾下啦<br />\n取下暖 放低心事 搵啲support"},{"pid":"da2d2a598fd30385c525c809e8c5550aceecc68d","tid":430842,"uid":84025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"巴打不如試下5-htp<br />\n我輕度depression唔想食藥<br />\n食完呢隻supplement 好左好多<br />\n你可以上網睇下資料先決定食唔食<br />\n我見佢幫到ADHD添<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livestrong.com%2Farticle%2F485787-5-htp-for-adhd%2F&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f759eea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/</a>"},{"pid":"a334cfabdf449fa304669b6580be7819445db837","tid":430842,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同樓主好似<br />\n呢排仲要多左social anxiety <br />\n好辛苦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n訂緊nootropic 5htp呢啲<br />\n不過唔知會唔會治標唔治本"},{"pid":"58a72941c9d6219b0c9bfbb0e525484e79a837c8","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打不如試下5-htp<br />\n我輕度depression唔想食藥<br />\n食完呢隻supplement 好左好多<br />\n你可以上網睇下資料先決定食唔食<br />\n我見佢幫到ADHD添<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livestrong.com%2Farticle%2F485787-5-htp-for-adhd%2F&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f759eea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咦、頭上兩位巴打都講 5-HTP、我今日第一次知有依樣野。 巴打有係食過可唔可以分享一下有無用/ 有無咩副作用。<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇左依隻好似香港好似無註冊做成藥。應該算係健康產品/ supplement, right? <br />\n<br />\n您地訂邊款、如果有用我都真心想試下、因為始終睇醫生真係最後一步。"},{"pid":"eb0dd5a213f8b47da12da055ebbe29b854f2b46a","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同樓主好似<br />\n呢排仲要多左social anxiety <br />\n好辛苦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n訂緊nootropic 5htp呢啲<br />\n不過唔知會唔會治標唔治本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你係咪講依隻？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/203613_a8aab1beba32f96298bc1e1f0730fa21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F203613_a8aab1beba32f96298bc1e1f0730fa21.jpg&h=44fadca7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81f97d84c31543fa5740a3b517eab6e6594c7f52","tid":430842,"uid":84025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打不如試下5-htp<br />\n我輕度depression唔想食藥<br />\n食完呢隻supplement 好左好多<br />\n你可以上網睇下資料先決定食唔食<br />\n我見佢幫到ADHD添<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livestrong.com%2Farticle%2F485787-5-htp-for-adhd%2F&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f759eea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咦、頭上兩位巴打都講 5-HTP、我今日第一次知有依樣野。 巴打有係食過可唔可以分享一下有無用/ 有無咩副作用。<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇左依隻好似香港好似無註冊做成藥。應該算係健康產品/ supplement, right? <br />\n<br />\n您地訂邊款、如果有用我都真心想試下、因為始終睇醫生真係最後一步。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係iherb買既<br />\n佢有隻time release<br />\nLong lasting 好多<br />\n我自己食完就冇乜點發現有副作用<br />\n不過人人唔同<br />\n你可以試下食少少先"},{"pid":"7317ccda2c333ed8aee749e03d0d6ee2082f9219","tid":430842,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"請問樓主係未睇醫生嘅情況下 會覺得自己有中度抑鬱呢 點衡量出係中度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6163b63b2c7ce8002f8dc4fa58c43fe7254cec93","tid":430842,"uid":112850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"其實睇公立確診左精神病，係咪會留底咁就一世架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 想睇公立診所refer我去精神科"},{"pid":"ee7de12474b1b0cd8683e1c9a1b537cd660fed71","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問樓主係未睇醫生嘅情況下 會覺得自己有中度抑鬱呢 點衡量出係中度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我係網上做過一d網上評估、<br />\n我知係唔準、或者 non-conclusive,<br />\n但我出來做結果都係算high end...<br />\n我無自殺傾向、嚴重失眠及/或無端端喊、所以知道自己唔係重度囉...而於點解係中度、<br />\n因為我個情況都持續左兩年以上、<br />\n基於以上原因、我推論可能係低至中度、<br />\n我個標題可能有potential misleading/ 錯既地方、I say jo sorry sin<br />\n但我只係想問下巴打們既意見"},{"pid":"b119332c0a710409087d4cd9ccd67c538a9061d9","tid":430842,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"中度左四五年，開始有自殺念頭<br />\n屋企人知嘛"},{"pid":"69a1d46e398a1168bd58512d24b51e45a4d3f0b3","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問樓主係未睇醫生嘅情況下 會覺得自己有中度抑鬱呢 點衡量出係中度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n您可唔可以分享下您既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對無/輕/中/重既相關徵狀無專業既認識、<br />\n亦都唔覺得佢地之間會有一個好明確既界定方式、<br />\n求指教、因為我自己都唔知道應唔應該行到睇精神科醫生依一步。"},{"pid":"d1d5ce4ef4d839410f4380aa17047b945eeccd13","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中度左四五年，開始有自殺念頭<br />\n屋企人知嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你有無睇醫生？<br />\n個情況is getting worst !? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頂住呀巴打、唔好做傻事"},{"pid":"4a50a699e40568d4a8715062e3d64f7b3e2eb105","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打不如試下5-htp<br />\n我輕度depression唔想食藥<br />\n食完呢隻supplement 好左好多<br />\n你可以上網睇下資料先決定食唔食<br />\n我見佢幫到ADHD添<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livestrong.com%2Farticle%2F485787-5-htp-for-adhd%2F&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f759eea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.livestrong.com/article/485787-5-htp-for-adhd/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咦、頭上兩位巴打都講 5-HTP、我今日第一次知有依樣野。 巴打有係食過可唔可以分享一下有無用/ 有無咩副作用。<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇左依隻好似香港好似無註冊做成藥。應該算係健康產品/ supplement, right? <br />\n<br />\n您地訂邊款、如果有用我都真心想試下、因為始終睇醫生真係最後一步。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係iherb買既<br />\n佢有隻time release<br />\nLong lasting 好多<br />\n我自己食完就冇乜點發現有副作用<br />\n不過人人唔同<br />\n你可以試下食少少先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽日即刻訂d試下"},{"pid":"a256a4ef93af40dc33abbf6dc85f5a079bb389ab","tid":430842,"uid":64972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"你有冇同朋友傾訴過自己心情呀？<br />\n知唔知係乜原因令自己唔太開心？"},{"pid":"7e731072f3df8f8196e1707bb7f126c77592dadb","tid":430842,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"講真，去外國隊半年草啦"},{"pid":"3bd4d2a632bb31cb2b93f2d4059f612c0570e119","tid":430842,"uid":85307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"私家未同公立嘅資料庫同步<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"703af33cc62c5dbcd717de3c05c6bd5c5a643ee8","tid":430842,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有冇同朋友傾訴過自己心情呀？<br />\n知唔知係乜原因令自己唔太開心？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有既<br />\n其實女朋友都知我唔開心左好耐、<br />\n<br />\n我估應該係因為長久以來來自工作上同屋企既壓力、<br />\n加上愈來愈覺得自己人生有無力感、亦都無fulfillment、唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65041807e4114cc2036829cad78d5bda597c79a9","tid":430842,"uid":80777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打、內文有少少長、<br />\n但希望您地耐心睇完的話可以比少少意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔開心左好耐、<br />\n計計埋埋都有兩年以上。<br />\n<br />\n我唔會無端端喊果d、<br />\n但係每日都好唔開心 感覺人生好灰暗<br />\n我無自殺既念頭、<br />\n但感覺人生、將來無咩野好憧景<br />\n感覺人生好無趣、好無意義。<br />\n死左都不太可惜果種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n訓得OK, 無咩失眠問題、<br />\n但有嗜睡問題、<br />\n我愈來愈少講野、<br />\n有時個人會好呆、<br />\n記性明顯差左好多、<br />\n無論係訓8個鐘好、定係4個半鍾好、都好累好累<br />\n<br />\n我一直都唔想面對有一日要去睇醫生依個情況<br />\n我有試過食EPA補充劑再加跑步去解決一直情緒低落既問題、<br />\n跑完係有感覺好左、<br />\n但之後又變番唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n我想去見精神科醫生、私家果d。<br />\n我知道如果去睇政府醫生、我響公立醫院既病歷就會有抑鬱症(如果醫生確診)跟我一世、以後一世唔駛考紀律部隊。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係諗住考紀律部隊、我本身係會計師。<br />\n如果我自己去睇私家醫生開d抗抑鬱藥試下食。<br />\n依個情況之下、我會唔會響個人病歷中留有被確診抑鬱性/ 情緒病紀錄？<br />\n因為我將來可能會考財金類既公務員、或者移民之類、怕因爲咁樣成世就花左個紀錄。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錢的話可以試下私家臨床心理輔導"},{"pid":"0423dc6c164df4b245d4643607a5d2b3d4163b95","tid":430842,"uid":85307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"去外國用啲psychedelic醫啦 好多都醫到"},{"pid":"96779645326042ebbf2d95bd039673b81c840e23","tid":430842,"uid":32437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"病向淺中醫<br />\n我當你暪盡天下人<br />\n你得到想要嘅野果陣仲有無命享先<br />\n<br />\n有個寓言係有個人拎住粒雞蛋<br />\n就幻想諗自己黎緊要開牧場，起大屋，娶妾侍<br />\n你同個主角無分別<br />\n仲要以為自己唔醫病就會幻想成真"},{"pid":"84091897fad254ca06f0095bf3a473f2061d9484","tid":430842,"uid":139136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"巴打如果你唔想留底就睇私家比較好d<br />\nHA的話你住院定門診睇都一樣有記錄<br />\n不過其實樓上都講中point<br />\n你考慮改善左自己心理健康先考慮咩工啦Ching"},{"pid":"919aa1938a270fd2942adba32c6334e9bf520e7f","tid":430842,"uid":152527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T17:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打、內文有少少長、<br />\n但希望您地耐心睇完的話可以比少少意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔開心左好耐、<br />\n計計埋埋都有兩年以上。<br />\n<br />\n我唔會無端端喊果d、<br />\n但係每日都好唔開心 感覺人生好灰暗<br />\n我無自殺既念頭、<br />\n但感覺人生、將來無咩野好憧景<br />\n感覺人生好無趣、好無意義。<br />\n死左都不太可惜果種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n訓得OK, 無咩失眠問題、<br />\n但有嗜睡問題、<br />\n我愈來愈少講野、<br />\n有時個人會好呆、<br />\n記性明顯差左好多、<br />\n無論係訓8個鐘好、定係4個半鍾好、都好累好累<br />\n<br />\n我一直都唔想面對有一日要去睇醫生依個情況<br />\n我有試過食EPA補充劑再加跑步去解決一直情緒低落既問題、<br />\n跑完係有感覺好左、<br />\n但之後又變番唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n我想去見精神科醫生、私家果d。<br />\n我知道如果去睇政府醫生、我響公立醫院既病歷就會有抑鬱症(如果醫生確診)跟我一世、以後一世唔駛考紀律部隊。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係諗住考紀律部隊、我本身係會計師。<br />\n如果我自己去睇私家醫生開d抗抑鬱藥試下食。<br />\n依個情況之下、我會唔會響個人病歷中留有被確診抑鬱性/ 情緒病紀錄？<br />\n因為我將來可能會考財金類既公務員、或者移民之類、怕因爲咁樣成世就花左個紀錄。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以睇私家咪無record , depression 係香港好正常"},{"pid":"cad0ab51e454a36355187d8a41b2edc20ad1405d","tid":430842,"uid":45999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"我都成日諗自殺"},{"pid":"2d251fc7e1caa88a5954a333f0443bff12e68a6a","tid":430842,"uid":128916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:11:36.000Z","msg":"自己食藥唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港有好多機構有心理輔導/治療<br />\n價錢700/800一個鐘起左右<br />\n撐住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fe96d8df0f83d1dc6ace3d0ba3a6eb0c106b6a","tid":430842,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:33:11.000Z","msg":"做會計壓力大姐<br />\n西藥邊會醫到抑鬱丫<br />\n心病還需心藥醫，點醫就睇你自己喇"},{"pid":"3d1df11b05143a23279b63d2c1a02462a1d6514b","tid":430842,"uid":55051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"點解會覺得自己有adhd?<br />\n我岩岩睇左公立adhd"},{"pid":"6cd36d8cb61538d857030acf4d513a38c1ed056f","tid":430842,"uid":84025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"樓主而家點？有冇好轉？"},{"pid":"e0e2559d81c2fc6b8da6aee6c34c089930099bcb","tid":430842,"uid":65406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"我都有呢D情況,一有生活壓力就發作,事情過左明明自覺應該無壓力.但個天都仲係灰色.各方面能力下降.好唔想地做左5日野,兩日放假只係等星期一番工,D所謂減壓活動我都無哂興趣做.我都怕再挨多一兩年會灰到去死<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係自從家人離世後慢慢開始.感覺世界越來越重<br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該去睇醫生/評估?"},{"pid":"b5bdfd33d778de4961a7d20b50871602fad635e4","tid":430842,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521d98586aa260b5832b78edcad026bc59b4fb55","tid":430842,"uid":50032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"呢d病如果落左政府record, 以後唔會有政府工請<br />\n幾年前起家庭醫生睇完(depression) ，轉介左去旺角中心，之後食左一年藥，一個月差唔多二千幾，停左就無再睇。"},{"pid":"11cfee32a7577a3425e935f755e651092ad5238f","tid":430842,"uid":50032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實睇公立確診左精神病，係咪會留底咁就一世架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 想睇公立診所refer我去精神科</blockquote><br />\n個時做認知治療同行為治療，加食藥"},{"pid":"495c2962c146b0ccc951fc70cda10dc2f51363d5","tid":430842,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"建議睇下書 同人傾下<br />\n好過睇醫生<br />\n啲醫生好唔得閑 冇真係醫緊你 只係開藥比你 <br />\n你需要既係counsellor ，clinical psychologist 等等，如果你係想解心結（而覺得身邊朋友唔適合）既話"},{"pid":"5da8401fb7237b109aa133d30a71beba7ee7747e","tid":430842,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"Depression Treatment<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.helpguide.org/articles/depression/depression-treatment.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.helpguide.org%2Farticles%2Fdepression%2Fdepression-treatment.htm&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7e94faaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.helpguide.org/articles/depression/depression-treatment.htm</a>"}]}